## Global input bindings for X

# Screenshots
Print
  screenshot

# Brightness and audo

XF86MonBrightnessDown
  xbacklight -dec 15
XF86MonBrightnessUp
  xbacklight -inc 15
XF86AudioMute
  amixer set Master toggle
XF86AudioLowerVolume
  amixer set Master 3dB-
XF86AudioRaiseVolume
  amixer set Master 3dB+

